imdb.plot outline: Lagansiders" is a new 6 part online drama serial from Belfast, Northern Ireland. The 6 episode's will explore the trials and tribulations of life for a group of individuals who live in a community housing block in Belfast. The characters have a mixture of religious and cultural beliefs. Some of the characters will be affected with events such as unemployment, alcoholism, homelessness, poverty, infidelity amongst others.
